Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------ANIME-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹  你有空吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要和我去玩玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,325)\fs14}doppelg?nger
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道「分身」一说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分…？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要是看见了  灾厄将会降临其身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  瞎说啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅呆了  你看见他那表情了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.59,0:01:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和他说了几句话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他自己就对号入座了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.17,0:01:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫针眼来着？眼皮都肿了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该很快就会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒是  不过很不方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个月就升到三年级了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.53,0:03:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  到时候也十五岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不是不好  觉得没什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如中考之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  别让我想起来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件是不是太花俏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点土
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？我倒是不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要买给我的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我要穿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用老是照镜子很轻松吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这用法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮廓不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着有点来气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真土
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像「来辨真假」一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  你好像说过能看见什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我身上也能看到什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这双眼  我觉得很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右眼的颜色不同感觉很美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是叫异色症来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫双色瞳啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮起来太浪费了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多可爱的脸蛋就这么白费了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这不是在绕着弯子说自己也可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这我不否定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  给我那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？为什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  那只娃娃那么可爱的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未咲对可爱的认知有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个可爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个丑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那边的象呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不懂你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去更好一点的游乐园啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周妈妈因为人偶的展览会要去东京  所以不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我得一个人看家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姨妈不在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就去你家玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月天还下雪真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣真幸福  家里有好多漂亮的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟姐妹  算不算二代血亲来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血亲？啊是的  二代血亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈和爸爸是一代血亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷奶奶是二代血亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兄弟姐妹应该也是二代血亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新的班级里  那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有在传这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  新的班级怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有帅哥吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是觉得  这个班级有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点像「被诅咒了」的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被诅咒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这种类似的传言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那确实有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没帅哥吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要给你介绍一个？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介绍啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  男生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说没帅哥吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未咲  你像做媒人的大妈一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是大妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里我还是头一次来  好壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是幸代姨妈做的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈呢  希望你能原谅她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指光代姨妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是姨妈  也是你妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么原谅不原谅的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈现在还把鸣当做自己的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也真的很想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过因为让别人收养你  心里感到愧疚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有让鸣离开自己身边而产生的罪恶感  所以说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道她很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有埋怨过她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要说到心里感到愧疚的话  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾果…妈妈也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从双胞胎姐妹那里夺走了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  更多的是害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心我会回到我亲身母亲身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也禁止我们俩见面？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的想法也可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不习惯的话  这个地方待久了可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去楼上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为人偶是空虚的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:09:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的房间就只有四畳半的空间外加一套被褥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想有这样一个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你也不是小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别摆姐姐的架子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是双胞胎  不分大小的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说先出世的就是姐姐么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该力气大的才是姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么理论…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是姐姐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勤劳少女可是很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在旁人看来就是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到蛮瘦的  放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:10:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我瘦可不代表你瘦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说啥  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢  发育了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别害羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未咲真是的  啥时候变成那种大叔了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们第几次一起洗澡来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候的就不记得了  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该有两三次吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从什么时候开始的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学五年级的时候来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  五年级的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天根婆婆一不小心说漏了嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是早就有点察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说也太像了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…也对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婴儿时候的照片一张也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我想不可能会丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在家里偷偷找了一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  刚出生时的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和鸣你并排照的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的长得一模一样  真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  明天去游乐场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我们以前和妈妈三个人一起去的游乐场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错  姨妈那次因为这事发了很大脾气  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真不明白那个时候她为什么那么生气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  就去那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣你有喜欢的人么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  未咲你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普普通通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普普通通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  看着很老实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:12:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果是喜欢摇滚的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的乐队一样是么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有什么契机之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记不大清了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  刚才你说勤劳少女了吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在打工么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  在附近的豆腐店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零用钱很紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机话费也不可小看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己玩的钱至少想要自己挣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未咲真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  马上就到爸爸的生日了  所以嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未咲和家人「相连」着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:15:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前来的时候还以为是个更大的游乐场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们长大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  时光的流逝可真残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去快要撞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是千钧一发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的鸣像姐姐一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔我来保护下未咲有何不可
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护什么的太夸张了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅是因为我的名字叫未咲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是因为作为养女被送出去  那眼睛也不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道以为是自己的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想法真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只眼睛是因为生病
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟养女什么的都无关  不是任何人的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不管是未咲还是爸爸妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没有丝毫怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也会想为什么只有我遭受这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我想结果还是一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  如果是未咲作为养女被送出去  又失去左眼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会像现在的未咲一样难过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在就挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  那边不就是未咲的家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜见山市真小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之还是得离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢大城市吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为学校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  我想学音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐大学？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是减肥了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  你比我还瘦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了  鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣也会跟着掉下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我绝不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保护未咲…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.06,0:18:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.53,0:18:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到那么不起眼的刺激项目居然会那么口怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你听懂了就行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前真害怕这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是挺喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.66,0:19:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣倒是意外的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的感觉么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为死定了  真尽兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说什么死的  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我都没活着的实感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在游乐场遇到那种事都没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那种担心的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫化疗吧？最近听说白血病是能治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎就算药不起作用还有叫骨髓移植的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话从我这里抽就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生也说从鸣身上抽是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出院之后再去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来马上就过生日了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么想要的么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.55,0:20:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣的生日也是一起的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.51,0:20:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要健康的未咲  如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是个难题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在鸣家里看到的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.77,0:21:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我尽力试试
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.68,0:22:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.97,0:22:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  我说你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣  见崎鸣
